{"tid":2488720,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 有冇人仲記得依件印堂發黑落仔MK妹?","createTime":"2021-04-14T12:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T14:39:11.000Z","uid":227275,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7835dedd601ecb245b7e86ee22d53fa249cebfff","tid":2488720,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/110010_760cf8033fd7483b03b71e1f30b2456e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F110010_760cf8033fd7483b03b71e1f30b2456e.jpg&h=b003de7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人爆料話佢真人D頭髮真係生到落額頭度 所以先P圖P成咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/111927_1b6cbbaf5d3e34144f2d0f8b42777c84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F111927_1b6cbbaf5d3e34144f2d0f8b42777c84.jpg&h=91be50da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紋身串錯字 但唔排除係留言條友懶醒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/113710_f5ffbf6ab54007a9f09be2484dd2c3fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F113710_f5ffbf6ab54007a9f09be2484dd2c3fd.jpg&h=62602465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最精彩係做倉但又扮有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/202137_9d370378c200778445652fad17afb6df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F202137_9d370378c200778445652fad17afb6df.jpg&h=caab48bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/202139_959f964c6d6685217a30515638034c43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F202139_959f964c6d6685217a30515638034c43.jpg&h=eac5235d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n月頭